All Classes

  • All Classes Class Summary Exception Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectionInitializationException
    Exception wrapper thrown when the connection to a web application could not be initialized.
    ConnectionTerminationException
    Exception wrapper thrown when the connection to a web application could not be terminated.
    GameStepParser
    Responsible for parsing the information of a single game step received from the webservice by transforming a JSON String to a GameStep.
    GameStepPlayer
    Simple Class which implements IPlayer and contains informations of players for a single GameStep.
    JettyHttpClientFactory
    Class responsible for wrapping the production of HttpClients with a SslContextFactory.
    JSONGameStep
    Class representing the JSON Object sent to each spe_ed client in a single game step.
    JSONGameStepPlayer
    Class representing a part of a JSONGameStep object, containing player specific information about each enemy and yourself.
    JSONResponse
    Object representing the JSON response send to the spe_ed server after a single game step.
    JSONServerTime
    Class representing the JSON response received from the spe_ed time API.
    MalformedURLException
    Exception wrapper thrown when the a URL has an invalid format.
    MessageSendingException
    Exception wrapper thrown when a webservice client tried to send a message, which could not be sent.
    ResponseParser
    Responsible for parsing the response to send to the spe_ed server from a given PlayerAction.
    ServerTimeParser
    Responsible for parsing a JSONServerTime.
    SpeedConnectionManager
    Class responsible for managing the life cycle of a game of spe_ed on a given server.
    SpeedWebSocket
    WebSocket annotated websocket to connect a webservice client to the spe_ed webservice.
    SpeedWebSocketClient
    A SpeedWebSocketClient to connect SpeedWebSocket.
    TimeAPIClient
    Class responsible for requesting the server time.
    TimeRequestException
    Exception thrown when the spe_ed time API could not be reached and no server time could be received.
    TimeSynchronizationManager
    Responsible for the synchronization of server time and client time.
    WebserviceConnectionURI
    A WebserviceConnectionURI allows the connection to a spe_ed webservice.
